title: Bug 4121 - JarExporter causes out of sync
description: Bug 4121 - JarExporter causes out of sync
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file the second time.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself.
SR: To reproduce the bug: 1. Export a directory (project) as a jar file. 2. Place the exported jar file in the same directory (project). 3. Overwrite the exported jar file with the same file. Observe the out of sync message.
